{"tid":102044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，解決香港住屋問題，就係減少外來人口，開發棕地，cut丁權","createTime":"2017-01-31T10:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T02:21:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"626fc4a623c9ad713a05e926828f94074770e062","tid":102044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"唔搞哩三樣先走去填海，搞效野公園<br />\n<br />\n我屌你啦"},{"pid":"ec5560e6998f5d37c6aa4595b3ab36845be43160","tid":102044,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:22:48.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n<br />\n但呢三件事任何一件都難搞<br />\n<br />\n最少, under而家呢個政權係做唔到"},{"pid":"de278c58dd3fe4bfb375e5e716c2ca9e1f0224a6","tid":102044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"過年少上，冇啦啦咁多人係到spin<br />\n<br />\n屌那星"},{"pid":"2e35b3a23dcd817de9bbdcbc65a9afeda7f36ee2","tid":102044,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"班泛民打手唔會推呢post"},{"pid":"ec34d9a9d9b465554f13674815f77ed6a277208a","tid":102044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得好<br />\n<br />\n但呢三件事任何一件都難搞<br />\n<br />\n最少, under而家呢個政權係做唔到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主一樣唔會俾，所以應該唔要求，接受袋住先？<br />\n<br />\n唔做哩三樣先，就企硬唔俾搞郊野公園等"},{"pid":"587185958a860c13b26e35b343681a1f620d5d80","tid":102044,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"住屋問題只係暫時問題<br />\n<br />\n但係鏟效野公園就係永久嘅<br />\n<br />\n住屋仲有好多其他方向可以解決<br />\n<br />\n但係鏟9左郊野公園，以後就算真係俾你港獨到，過左幾百年之後香港都仲會係一個樣衰到爆嘅石屎森林 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b290118bd1c1c765cbf8cd3dddbe09ee5cfc140","tid":102044,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"呢個post好快俾人洗走"},{"pid":"4552ed965be478866dfae7b65a4f588511160e73","tid":102044,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"Cut丁權應該唔得啦 但頭果2個係應該要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0854535fd8b42703786df9d3bbbf9eb9dbb4a948","tid":102044,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"無撚錯，尤其係要減少外來人口。<br />\n日日佰五隻蝗走落嚟，貢獻唔到經濟仲要攞盡你社會福利。"},{"pid":"53b3eb2eb617798c3bfd369522d87c3ea5e1427e","tid":102044,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"1. 每日150新移民<br />\n2. 地產商/新界鄉紳囤積既土地<br />\n3. 棕地<br />\n<br />\n政府任何一樣都唔會搞<br />\n算吧啦"},{"pid":"b1c1d82e4a759d34db420357af0f94587f2a0370","tid":102044,"uid":11359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"啱啊"},{"pid":"68755b92cf2c3126ff8cc6b3847ca4b418aa7f87","tid":102044,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"收空置税<br />\n先係重點"},{"pid":"8c27069c8bde16beabb0290bceb1cdd530c63a95","tid":102044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbff7c9de58de6ab45c75901de6137584887900","tid":102044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 每日150新移民<br />\n2. 地產商/新界鄉紳囤積既土地<br />\n3. 棕地<br />\n<br />\n政府任何一樣都唔會搞<br />\n算吧啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪反對搞郊野公園到底<br />\n<br />\n難得有個議題可以團結埋中產屌政府"},{"pid":"9d66b8ce056b9daf185773f768ed5ad2189e0f05","tid":102044,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 每日150新移民<b